verbose_text: For example, although both Th1 cells and Th1 cells with CTL potential expressed CD150 (encoded by Slamf1), a direct comparison of IFN-gamma + env specific CD4 + T cells that co-produced GzmB (IFN-gamma + GzmB +) with those that did not (IFN-gamma + GzmB -) revealed significantly higher CD150 expression in the former (XREF_FIG C).
